Task
Is it true that the given number is a positive even number?
Given an arbitrary number. Determine if it is a positive even number.
Create a variable number and assign it the value of an arbitrary integer. Create a variable isPositiveEven and assign it 
a boolean expression that evaluates to true if the number is even and positive, and false otherwise.

Solution
const number = 44;
const isPositiveEven = number % 2 === 0 && number >0;
